General Information
    Content-Type    : application/json
    Methot          : Post
    Default JSON Response
    {
        "result" : True||False,
        "msg" : "test"
    }

/
    DEFINATION
        Test if server is running

    GET
        -

    RETURN
        "StuBC server is running!"


/user_register
    DEFINATION
        User registration. Adds new user to database.

    GET
        Params
        {
            "email" : "test",
            "password" : "test"
        }

    RETURN
        Default JSON Response


/user_login
    DEFINATION
        User login by username and password

    GET
        Params
        {
            "username" : "test",
            "password" : "test"
        }

    RETURN
        Default JSON Response


/user_recovery_password
    DEFINATION
        Recovers the user's password by sending new password to the user's email

    GET
        Params
        {
            "email" : "test"
        }

    RETURN
        Default JSON Response

/user_update_password
    DEFINATION
        Recovers the user's password by sending new password to the user's email

    GET
        Params
        {
            "username" : "test",
            "password" : "test",
            "new_password" : "test"
        }

    RETURN
        Default JSON Response